title: Guild Wars: The Complete Collection
description:
This complete set of guildwars all on one disc.

Format: ISO

Contains: 1: Prophecies
          2: Factions
          3: Nightfall
          4: Eye Of The North 
This is for people who already has guildwars but has(like i did) each game on separate discs, about 6 discs i think which took ages to install. but now with this all can be installed at once thanks to my brother buying the Guild Wars: The Complete Collection and lets me create a iso for all to have and share.

PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED YOUR OWN ACCOUNT TO PLAY. AND THIS IS FOR GUILDWARS ACCOUNT PEOPLE WHO HAVE A ACCOUNT ALREADY.
